> **What this document is.** The operational runbook for a security incident:
> who responds, how an incident is detected and rated, how it is contained and
> recovered, and — load-bearing for the review — the **mandatory duty to report
> a confirmed incident affecting Salesforce customer data to Salesforce within
> 24 hours.** A reviewer reads this for evidence that the duty is wired into a
> runbook *now*, not improvised during an incident.

